<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>개체 등록 · 보증서 발행 | ARK PROJECT</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root { --green:#1A3620; --gold:#D4AF37; --gold-soft:#E8D9A0; --paper:#FBF8F0; --line:rgba(212,175,55,0.22); }
    * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
    body { font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif; background:linear-gradient(160deg,#1A3620,#0E1F12); color:var(--paper); min-height:100vh; padding:26px 14px 60px; }
    .wrap { max-width:680px; margin:0 auto; }
    .top { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:18px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
    .logo { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; color:var(--gold); letter-spacing:3px; font-size:15px; }
    .nav a, .logout { color:var(--gold-soft); font-size:12px; text-decoration:none; border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.4); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:6px; background:none; cursor:pointer; margin-left:6px; }
    .nav a.active { background:var(--gold); color:#10220f; border-color:var(--gold); }
    .panel { background:rgba(0,0,0,0.22); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; }
    .section-head { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; background:rgba(212,175,55,0.10); padding:13px 18px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
    .section-head .dot { width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--gold); }
    .section-head h2 { font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:#fff; letter-spacing:0.5px; }
    .req-note { margin-left:auto; font-size:11px; color:var(--gold-soft); opacity:0.7; }
    table.form { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; }
    table.form tr { border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
    table.form tr:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    table.form th { width:32%; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding:14px 16px; font-weight:400; font-size:13px; color:var(--gold-soft); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    table.form th .star { color:var(--gold); margin-right:3px; }
    table.form td { padding:10px 16px; }
    input[type=text], textarea, select { width:100%; padding:11px 12px; border-radius:7px; font-size:14px; border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.30); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color:#fff; font-family:inherit; }
    select option { color:#000; }
    input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--gold); }
    textarea { resize:vertical; min-height:78px; line-height:1.6; }
    .hint { font-size:11px; color:var(--gold-soft); opacity:0.65; margin-top:5px; }
    .pair { display:flex; gap:10px; }
    .pair > div { flex:1; }
    .check { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:9px; font-size:14px; color:#fff; cursor:pointer; }
    .check input { width:18px; height:18px; accent-color:#D4AF37; }
    .quick { padding:16px 18px; }
    .quick textarea { min-height:96px; }
    .quick .qbtn { margin-top:10px; padding:10px 18px; border:none; border-radius:8px; background:rgba(212,175,55,0.18); color:var(--gold-soft); border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.5); font-size:13px; cursor:pointer; }
    .actions { margin-top:20px; }
    button.submit { width:100%; padding:15px; border:none; border-radius:9px; background:linear-gradient(180deg,#E6C75A,#D4AF37); color:#10220f; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1px; cursor:pointer; }
    .alert { padding:13px 15px; border-radius:8px; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .err { background:rgba(180,40,40,0.25); border:1px solid rgba(220,80,80,0.5); color:#ffd9d9; }
    .ok { background:rgba(40,120,60,0.25); border:1px solid rgba(120,200,140,0.5); color:#d6ffe0; }
    .ok .btns { margin-top:10px; }
    .ok .btns a { display:inline-block; margin-right:8px; font-size:13px; padding:8px 14px; border:1px solid var(--gold); border-radius:7px; color:var(--gold); text-decoration:none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="top">
      <div class="logo">ARK PROJECT · BY JIYANG</div>
      <div class="nav">
        <a href="/admin/new" class="active">개체 등록</a>
        <a href="/admin/plants">등록 내역</a>
        <a href="/admin">보증서 발송</a>
        <a href="/admin/logs">발송 내역</a>
        <form method="POST" action="/admin/logout" style="display:inline"><button class="logout" type="submit">로그아웃</button></form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %><div class="alert err">⚠️ <%= error %></div><% } %>
    <% if (result) { %>
      <div class="alert ok">
        ✅ <strong><%= result.고유번호 %></strong> · <%= result.품종명 %> 등록 완료!
        <div class="btns">
          <a href="<%= result.url %>" target="_blank">보증서 미리보기</a>
          <a href="/admin">이 번호로 발송하기 →</a>
          <a href="/admin/plants">등록 내역 보기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/admin/new">
      <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
        <div class="section-head"><span class="dot"></span><h2>빠른 입력 (붙여넣기)</h2></div>
        <div class="quick">
          <textarea id="paste" placeholder="엑셀/메모에서 4줄을 그대로 붙여넣으세요. 순서:&#10;1줄 고유번호 → 2줄 종(속명) → 3줄 영문명 → 4줄 품종명(한글)&#10;&#10;예)&#10;JY-SPRX-特715-26-RG760&#10;H.springboks hyb&#10;'Ma seong'&#10;'마성(魔星)'"></textarea>
          <div class="hint">붙여넣고 "자동 채우기"를 누르면 아래 고유번호·종·영문명·품종명 칸이 자동으로 입력됩니다. (작은따옴표는 자동 제거)</div>
          <button type="button" class="qbtn" onclick="autoFill()">↓ 자동 채우기</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
        <div class="section-head"><span class="dot"></span><h2>기본 정보</h2><span class="req-note">★ 필수 입력</span></div>
        <table class="form">
          <tr>
            <th><span class="star">★</span>고유번호 (제품번호)</th>
            <td>
              <input type="text" name="고유번호" value="<%= form['고유번호'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: JY-PYG-JY001-26-RG0761" required />
              <div class="hint">형식 예: JY-[계통]-[개체]-[연도]-RG[일련] · 중복 불가 · 다음 RG 추천: <b><%= nextSerial %></b></div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>등급</th>
            <td>
              <% var grades=['로얄골드','골드','레드','그린']; var sel=(form['등급']||'로얄골드'); %>
              <select name="등급">
                <% grades.forEach(function(g){ %><option value="<%= g %>" <%= sel===g?'selected':'' %>><%= g %></option><% }); %>
              </select>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><th><span class="star">★</span>품종명 (한글)</th><td><input type="text" name="품종명" value="<%= form['품종명'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: 마성(魔星)" required /></td></tr>
          <tr><th>영문명</th><td><input type="text" name="영문명" value="<%= form['영문명'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: Ma seong" /></td></tr>
          <tr><th>종 / 속명</th><td><input type="text" name="종" value="<%= form['종'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: H.springboks hyb" /></td></tr>
          <tr>
            <th>번식 구분</th>
            <td>
              <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="자구번식묘" value="예" <%= form['자구번식묘']==='예'?'checked':'' %> /> 자구 번식묘</label>
              <div class="hint">자구(새끼묘)로 번식한 개체이면 체크하세요.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><th>상태</th><td><input type="text" name="상태" value="<%= form['상태'] || '정품 인증' %>" placeholder="정품 인증" /></td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
        <div class="section-head"><span class="dot"></span><h2>육종 정보</h2></div>
        <table class="form">
          <tr><th>육종가</th><td><input type="text" name="육종가" value="<%= form['육종가'] || '지양하월시아' %>" /></td></tr>
          <tr><th>육종 연도</th><td><input type="text" name="육종연도" value="<%= form['육종연도'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: 2026" /></td></tr>
          <tr>
            <th>모본 · 부본</th>
            <td><div class="pair">
              <div><input type="text" name="모본" value="<%= form['모본'] || '' %>" placeholder="모본 (씨받이)" /></div>
              <div><input type="text" name="부본" value="<%= form['부본'] || '' %>" placeholder="부본 (꽃가루)" /></div>
            </div></td>
          </tr>
          <tr><th>DNA 마커</th><td><input type="text" name="DNA마커" value="<%= form['DNA마커'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: 등록완료 JY-DNA-0001" /></td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
        <div class="section-head"><span class="dot"></span><h2>사진 · 인증</h2></div>
        <table class="form">
          <tr><th>사진 URL</th><td><input type="text" name="사진URL" value="<%= form['사진URL'] || '' %>" placeholder="https://.../plant.jpg" /><div class="hint">.jpg / .png 권장. 비우면 '사진 준비 중' 표시.</div></td></tr>
          <tr><th>관리자 메시지</th><td><textarea name="관리자메시지" placeholder="비우면 기본 환영 문구"><%= form['관리자메시지'] || '' %></textarea></td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="section-head"><span class="dot"></span><h2>소유 정보</h2></div>
        <table class="form">
          <tr><th>현 소유자</th><td><input type="text" name="소유자" value="<%= form['소유자'] || '' %>" placeholder="예: 홍길동 (발송 시 자동 누적됩니다)" /></td></tr>
          <tr>
            <th>소유자 이전 기록</th>
            <td>
              <textarea name="소유이력" placeholder="한 줄에 하나씩. 형식: 날짜 | 내용"><%= form['소유이력'] || '' %></textarea>
              <div class="hint">보증서 발송으로 소유권이 바뀔 때마다 여기에 자동으로 한 줄씩 누적됩니다.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="actions"><button class="submit" type="submit">개체 등록하기</button></div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <script>
    function stripQuotes(s){ return (s||'').trim().replace(/^[‘’'"\s]+|[‘’'"\s]+$/g,'').trim(); }
    function setVal(name,val){ var el=document.getElementsByName(name)[0]; if(el && val) el.value=val; }
    function autoFill(){
      var raw=(document.getElementById('paste').value||'').trim();
      if(!raw){ return; }
      var parts=raw.split(/\r?\n/).map(function(s){return s.trim();}).filter(function(s){return s;});
      if(parts.length<2){ parts=raw.split(/\t/).map(function(s){return s.trim();}).filter(function(s){return s;}); }
      // 순서: 고유번호, 종(속명), 영문명, 품종명
      if(parts[0]) setVal('고유번호', stripQuotes(parts[0]));
      if(parts[1]) setVal('종', stripQuotes(parts[1]));
      if(parts[2]) setVal('영문명', stripQuotes(parts[2]));
      if(parts[3]) setVal('품종명', stripQuotes(parts[3]));
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
